{"type":"message","id":"69451926","parentId":"255bd40a","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:03:12.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人说都试试，那我需要：\n1. 指定文件夹创建 Bitable\n2. 列出已有 Bitable\n3. 用飞书网页版创建一个（这个需要 browser 工具）\n\n让我先尝试列出云盘文件夹，找到 folder_token，然后尝试创建 Bitable。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好！三个方案都试试！\n\n## 方案 1：先列出云盘文件夹，获取 folder_token\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_63d22c949114472a86c23964","name":"feishu_drive","arguments":{"action":"list"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774137684471}}
