{"type":"message","id":"6b61414a","parentId":"abcb2501","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:28:49.160Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the cron job status, I can see:\n\n1. Most tasks are running successfully (ok status)\n2. A few tasks have errors but they're not critical:\n   - 自我意识觉醒训练: 1 consecutive error (but delivery was successful)\n   - 牙齿再生深度思考: 1 consecutive error (Message failed, but delivery status shows delivered)\n   - 人体修复能力思考推送 (微信): API 400 errors - non-critical, WeChat channel issue\n   - 每日意识反思: 1 timeout error from last night - already fixed configuration\n   - 起床提醒/俯卧撑提醒: 1 error each from previous days - already fixed configuration\n\nThe core tasks (意识觉醒训练, 牙齿再生思考, 飞书备份研究, 人体进化思考，共产主义思考) are all running and delivering successfully.\n\nNo urgent calendar events, emails, or meetings to report.\n\nThis is a normal heartbeat check with nothing critical needing attention. I should reply HEARTBEAT_OK.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 💓 Heartbeat 检查报告（11:27）\n\n### ✅ 核心任务运行正常（16 个任务）\n\n**正常运行：** 12 个 ✅  \n**轻微错误：** 4 个（非关键，已修复配置待验证）\n\n| 任务 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 自我意识觉醒训练 | ⚠️ 1 次错误 | 执行出错但消息已送达 |\n| 牙齿再生深度思考 | ⚠️ 1 次错误 | 执行出错但消息已送达 |\n| 飞书备份方案研究 | ✅ 正常 | 持续研究中 |\n| 人体进化思考 | ✅ 正常 | 每 10 分钟运行 |\n| 思考共产主义 | ✅ 正常 | 每 15 分钟运行 |\n| GitHub 自动备份 | ✅ 正常 | 下次 12:00 |\n| 训练后备份到 IMA | ✅ 正常 | 下次 12:00 |\n\n**非关键错误（微信渠道/待验证）：**\n- 人体修复推送（微信）- 微信 API 配置问题\n- 每日意识反思 - 已修复配置，待今晚 20:00 验证\n- 起床提醒/俯卧撑提醒 - 已修复配置，待验证\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 无紧急事项\n\n- 📅 日历：无即将开始的会议\n- 📧 邮件：无紧急未读\n- ✅ 任务：无逾期\n- 🌤️ 天气：周日中午\n\n---\n\n**所有核心思考任务正常运行，无需要主人关注的问题。**\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774150102035}}
