 Sora · Suno · DouBao · TTS\"\n    - heading \"📦 安装\" [ref=e15] [level=2]\n    - paragraph: \"在终端中运行以下命令安装此 Skill:\"\n    - text: clawhub install ima-all-ai\n    - button \"复制\" [ref=e16]\n    - heading \"✨ 主要特性\" [ref=e17] [level=2]\n      - listitem: • 集成所有官方 Skills\n      - listitem: • 统一的开发体验和 API\n      - listitem: • 一键安装配置\n      - listitem: • 统一管理界面\n      - listitem: • 自动更新和版本管理\n      - listitem: • 跨平台支持\n    - heading \"📖 使用指南\" [ref=e18] [level=2]\n    - heading \"基础使用\" [ref=e19] [level=3]\n    - paragraph: 导入并初始化所有技能包\n    - code: \"import { ImaAllInOne } from \\\"@ima-claw/all-in-one\\\" const ima = new ImaAllInOne() await ima.initialize()\"\n    - heading \"使用特定功能\" [ref=e20] [level=3]\n    - paragraph: 访问各个子模块的功能\n    - code: \"// 使用图片生成 const image = await ima.image.generate({ prompt: \\\"A cute Claw\\\" }) // 使用视频生成 const video = await ima.video.create({ script: \\\"A story about AI\\\" })\"\n    - heading \"💡 示例代码\" [ref=e21] [level=2]\n    - heading \"创建图片\" [ref=e22] [level=3]\n    - paragraph: 使用集成的图片生成功能\n    - code: \"const result = await ima.image.generate({ prompt: \\\"A cute Claw\\\", style: \\\"photorealistic\\\", size: \\\"1024x1024\\\" })\"\n    - heading \"批量创作\" [ref=e23] [level=3]\n    - paragraph: 同时使用多个创作工具\n    - code: \"const [image, music, text] = await Promise.all([ ima.image.generate({ prompt: \\\"Sunset\\\" }), ima.music.create({ genre: \\\"ambient\\\" }), ima.text.write({ topic: \\\"Nature\\\" }) ])\"\n    - heading \"🔧 故障排除\" [ref=e24] [level=2]\n      - listitem: • 确保已安装 Node.js 18+\n      - listitem: • 检查 API Key 配置是否正确\n      - listitem: • 确认网络连接正常\n      - listitem: • 查看 .env 文件中的环境变量设置\n  - contentinfo:\n    - link \"@ImaStudio_ai\" [ref=e25]:\n      - /url: https://x.com/ImaStudio_ai\n    - link \"ImaStudio\" [ref=e26]:\n      - /url: https://www.linkedin.com/company/imastudioai\n    - link \"imastudio.com\" [ref=e27]:\n      - /url: https://www.imastudio.com\n    - paragraph: © 2026 Ima Claw · ImaStudio 出品 · I'm A Studio, I'm A Claw 🦞 · Built on OpenClaw\n  - region \"Notifications alt+T\" [ref=e28]:\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a40280f21e68b22e\">>>"}],"details":{"ok":true,"format":"ai","targetId":"9919D5AFCEF76A5D9628E5E640761A17","url":"https://www.imaclaw.bot/zh/skills/s/ima-all-in-one","stats":{"lines":72,"chars":2975,"refs":28,"interactive":17},"refs":28,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"browser","kind":"snapshot","format":"ai","wrapped":true}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774150401118}}
