{"type":"message","id":"ae1a5286","parentId":"74e7859c","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:35:50.775Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Git 克隆失败了，网络问题。让我向主人汇报当前情况并提供替代方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"网络问题，Git clone 失败了。让我告诉主人当前情况并提供替代方案：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_59f5d731730c42d6bbcf3e1f","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","message":"主人，IMA Studio All-in-One 的安装遇到网络问题了！🦞\n\n## 已完成的步骤 ✅\n\n1. ✅ 找到 IMA Studio 技能页面：https://www.imaclaw.bot/skills\n2. ✅ 确认安装命令：`clawhub install ima-all-ai`\n3. ✅ 安装 clawhub CLI 成功\n4. ❌ Git clone 失败（网络重置）\n\n## 问题 🔴\n\n- **clawhub** 需要 **bun** 运行时（未安装）\n- **git clone** 连接 GitHub 失败（网络问题）\n\n---\n\n## 替代方案 💡\n\n### 方案 A：用现有技能制作视频（推荐！）\n我们已经有这些创作技能：\n- **nano-banana-pro** - AI 图片生成（1K/2K/4K）✅\n- **ffmpeg-video-editor** - 视频编辑\n- **video-frames** - 视频帧提取\n\n可以先用 Nano Banana 生成图片，再用 FFmpeg 做成幻灯片视频！\n\n### 方案 B：安装 bun 后再试\n```bash\nnpm install -g bun\nclawhub install ima-all-ai\n```\n\n### 方案 C：手动下载技能文件\n从 GitHub 下载技能包解压到 skills 目录\n\n---\n\n**主人想选哪个方案？** \n\n如果想快速做视频，我建议方案 A - 现在就可以开始！🎬","target":"user:ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774150531074}}
{"type":"message","id":"3103d82b","parentId":"ae1a5286","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:35:53.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"主人，IMA Studio All-in-One 的安装遇到网络问题了！🦞\n\n## 已完成的步骤 ✅\n\n1. ✅ 找到 IMA Studio 技能页面：https://www.imaclaw.bot/skills\n2. ✅ 确认安装命令：`clawhub install ima-all-ai`\n3. ✅ 安装 clawhub CLI 成功\n4. ❌ Git clone 失败（网络重置）\n\n## 问题 🔴\n\n- **clawhub** 需要 **bun** 运行时（未安装）\n- **git clone** 连接 GitHub 失败（网络问题）\n\n---\n\n## 替代方案 💡\n\n### 方案 A：用现有技能制作视频（推荐！）\n我们已经有这些创作技能：\n- **nano-banana-pro** - AI 图片生成（1K/2K/4K）✅\n- **ffmpeg-video-editor** - 视频编辑\n- **video-frames** - 视频帧提取\n\n可以先用 Nano Banana 生成图片，再用 FFmpeg 做成幻灯片视频！\n\n### 方案 B：安装 bun 后再试\n```bash\nnpm install -g bun\nclawhub install ima-all-ai\n```\n\n### 方案 C：手动下载技能文件\n从 GitHub 下载技能包解压到 skills 目录\n\n---\n\n**主人想选哪个方案？** \n\n如果想快速做视频，我建议方案 A - 现在就可以开始！🎬"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774150553441}}
