{"type":"message","id":"5da536f7","parentId":"f26a8454","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:47:46.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"网络请求也失败了。让我告诉主人当前情况并提供替代方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e7766f539b714cb5a3ba7038","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","message":"主人，视频生成遇到技术问题了！🎬\n\n## 问题汇总 🔴\n\n1. **generate-video 技能** - 需要 gemskills 插件（npm 404，无法安装）\n2. **浏览器** - 超时错误，Gateway 可能需要重启\n3. **网页版** - 网络请求失败\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案 💡\n\n### 方案 A：重启 Gateway 后用浏览器（推荐）\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n重启后我可以用浏览器打开：\n- Gemini 2.5 Pro（支持文生视频）\n- SeeDream 网页版\n- Kling AI 网页版\n\n### 方案 B：安装 Python + nano-banana-pro\n安装 Python 环境，用已有的 nano-banana-pro 技能生成图片，然后用 FFmpeg 做成视频\n\n### 方案 C：用在线工具手动生成\n我帮主人找到以下免费/试用工具：\n- **Gemini 2.5 Pro** - gemini.google.com（支持视频生成）\n- **Kling AI** - klingai.com（专业 AI 视频）\n- **Runway ML** - runwayml.com（文生视频）\n- **Pika Labs** - pika.art（AI 视频）\n\n---\n\n**主人想：**\n1. 重启 Gateway 让我用浏览器生成？\n2. 还是我提供在线工具链接，主人手动生成？\n3. 或者先安装 Python 用图片 + FFmpeg 方案？\n\n等主人指示！🦞","target":"user:ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774151223897}}
{"type":"message","id":"4039c0bc","parentId":"5da536f7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:47:48.849Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"主人，视频生成遇到技术问题了！🎬\n\n## 问题汇总 🔴\n\n1. **generate-video 技能** - 需要 gemskills 插件（npm 404，无法安装）\n2. **浏览器** - 超时错误，Gateway 可能需要重启\n3. **网页版** - 网络请求失败\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案 💡\n\n### 方案 A：重启 Gateway 后用浏览器（推荐）\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n重启后我可以用浏览器打开：\n- Gemini 2.5 Pro（支持文生视频）\n- SeeDream 网页版\n- Kling AI 网页版\n\n### 方案 B：安装 Python + nano-banana-pro\n安装 Python 环境，用已有的 nano-banana-pro 技能生成图片，然后用 FFmpeg 做成视频\n\n### 方案 C：用在线工具手动生成\n我帮主人找到以下免费/试用工具：\n- **Gemini 2.5 Pro** - gemini.google.com（支持视频生成）\n- **Kling AI** - klingai.com（专业 AI 视频）\n- **Runway ML** - runwayml.com（文生视频）\n- **Pika Labs** - pika.art（AI 视频）\n\n---\n\n**主人想：**\n1. 重启 Gateway 让我用浏览器生成？\n2. 还是我提供在线工具链接，主人手动生成？\n3. 或者先安装 Python 用图片 + FFmpeg 方案？\n\n等主人指示！🦞"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774151268849}}
