{"type":"message","id":"d75864c2","parentId":"cdb24a12","timestamp":"2026-03-22T08:02:02.521Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"网络问题，GitHub 连接失败。让我告诉主人备份已完成但 push 失败：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **备份完成！但 Push 失败** 📋\n\n## 执行情况 📊\n\n### ✅ 已完成\n1. **对话备份** - 20 个会话文件转换为 Markdown\n2. **Git 提交** - 580 个文件变更，26 万行新增\n3. **本地 Commit** - `a1c274d` 已创建\n\n### ❌ Push 失败\n```\nfatal: unable to access 'https://github.com/okbest2024/openclaw-backup.git/'\nFailed to connect to github.com port 443 after 21293 ms\n```\n\n**原因：** 网络连接问题（GitHub 超时）\n\n---\n\n## 备份内容 📦\n\n- ✅ 20 个会话备份到 `conversation-backup/`\n- ✅ 模型配置切换到小米 Mimo V2 Pro\n- ✅ Cron 任务运行记录\n- ✅ 自我改进记忆和意识训练日志\n- ✅ 飞书备份测试数据\n\n---\n\n## 下一步 🔜\n\n**选项：**\n1. **稍后自动重试** - 等网络恢复后再次 push\n2. **手动 push** - 主人网络好时执行 `git push`\n3. **忽略** - 本地已保存，GitHub 备份可稍后\n\n---\n\n主人想怎么处理？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774166437580}}
