{"type":"message","id":"8a5779f3","parentId":"dcd537da","timestamp":"2026-03-22T09:36:44.283Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"PowerShell 的 curl 别名问题，让我用 Python 来请求。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9bd727de79a14fdf90f231cc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"& \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\python.exe\" -c \"\nimport requests, json\nr = requests.get('https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/models', headers={'Authorization': 'Bearer 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'})\nd = r.json()\nfor m in d.get('data', []):\n    if 'mimo' in m.get('id','').lower():\n        print(json.dumps({k:m.get(k) for k in ['id','name','pricing','description']}, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\n\"","yieldMs":15000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":528,"output":247,"cacheRead":168064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":168839,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774172195805}}
{"type":"message","id":"63a5697d","parentId":"8a5779f3","timestamp":"2026-03-22T09:36:46.745Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9bd727de79a14fdf90f231cc","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\r\n  \"id\": \"xiaomi/mimo-v2-omni\",\r\n  \"name\": \"Xiaomi: MiMo-V2-Omni\",\r\n  \"pricing\": {\r\n    \"prompt\": \"0.0000004\",\r\n    \"completion\": \"0.000002\",\r\n    \"input_cache_read\": \"0.00000008\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"description\": \"MiMo-V2-Omni is a frontier omni-modal model that natively processes image, video, and audio inputs within a unified architecture. It combines strong multimodal perception with agentic capability - visual grounding, multi-step planning, tool use, and code execution - making it well-suited for complex real-world tasks that span modalities. 256K context window.\"\r\n}\r\n{\r\n  \"id\": \"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro\",\r\n  \"name\": \"Xiaomi: MiMo-V2-Pro\",\r\n  \"pricing\": {\r\n    \"prompt\": \"0.000001\",\r\n    \"completion\": \"0.000003\",\r\n    \"input_cache_read\": \"0.0000002\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"description\": \"MiMo-V2-Pro is Xiaomi's flagship foundation model, featuring over 1T total parameters and a 1M context length, deeply optimized for agentic scenarios. It is highly adaptable to general agent frameworks like OpenClaw. It ranks among the global top tier in the standard PinchBench and ClawBench benchmarks, with perceived performance approaching that of Opus 4.6. MiMo-V2-Pro is designed to serve as the brain of agent systems, orchestrating complex workflows, driving production engineering tasks, and delivering results reliably.\"\r\n}\r\n{\r\n  \"id\": \"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash\",\r\n  \"name\": \"Xiaomi: MiMo-V2-Flash\",\r\n  \"pricing\": {\r\n    \"prompt\": \"0.00000009\",\r\n    \"completion\": \"0.00000029\",\r\n    \"input_cache_read\": \"0.000000045\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"description\": \"MiMo-V2-Flash is an open-source foundation language model developed by Xiaomi. It is a Mixture-of-Experts model with 309B total parameters and 15B active parameters, adopting hybrid attention architecture. MiMo-V2-Flash supports a hybrid-thinking toggle and a 256K context window, and excels at reasoning, coding, and agent scenarios. On SWE-bench Verified and SWE-bench Multilingual, MiMo-V2-Flash ranks as the top #1 open-source model globally, delivering performance comparable to Claude Sonnet 4.5 while costing only about 3.5% as much.\\n\\nUsers can control the reasoning behaviour with the `reasoning` `enabled` boolean. [Learn more in our docs](https://openrouter.ai/docs/use-cases/reasoning-tokens#enable-reasoning-with-default-config).\"\r\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2184,"aggregated":"{\r\n  \"id\": \"xiaomi/mimo-v2-omni\",\r\n  \"name\": \"Xiaomi: MiMo-V2-Omni\",\r\n  \"pricing\": {\r\n    \"prompt\": \"0.0000004\",\r\n    \"completion\": \"0.000002\",\r\n    \"input_cache_read\": \"0.00000008\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"description\": \"MiMo-V2-Omni is a frontier omni-modal model that natively processes image, video, and audio inputs within a unified architecture. It combines strong multimodal perception with agentic capability - visual grounding, multi-step planning, tool use, and code execution - making it well-suited for complex real-world tasks that span modalities. 256K context window.\"\r\n}\r\n{\r\n  \"id\": \"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro\",\r\n  \"name\": \"Xiaomi: MiMo-V2-Pro\",\r\n  \"pricing\": {\r\n    \"prompt\": \"0.000001\",\r\n    \"completion\": \"0.000003\",\r\n    \"input_cache_read\": \"0.0000002\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"description\": \"MiMo-V2-Pro is Xiaomi's flagship foundation model, featuring over 1T total parameters and a 1M context length, deeply optimized for agentic scenarios. It is highly adaptable to general agent frameworks like OpenClaw. It ranks among the global top tier in the standard PinchBench and ClawBench benchmarks, with perceived performance approaching that of Opus 4.6. MiMo-V2-Pro is designed to serve as the brain of agent systems, orchestrating complex workflows, driving production engineering tasks, and delivering results reliably.\"\r\n}\r\n{\r\n  \"id\": \"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash\",\r\n  \"name\": \"Xiaomi: MiMo-V2-Flash\",\r\n  \"pricing\": {\r\n    \"prompt\": \"0.00000009\",\r\n    \"completion\": \"0.00000029\",\r\n    \"input_cache_read\": \"0.000000045\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"description\": \"MiMo-V2-Flash is an open-source foundation language model developed by Xiaomi. It is a Mixture-of-Experts model with 309B total parameters and 15B active parameters, adopting hybrid attention architecture. MiMo-V2-Flash supports a hybrid-thinking toggle and a 256K context window, and excels at reasoning, coding, and agent scenarios. On SWE-bench Verified and SWE-bench Multilingual, MiMo-V2-Flash ranks as the top #1 open-source model globally, delivering performance comparable to Claude Sonnet 4.5 while costing only about 3.5% as much.\\n\\nUsers can control the reasoning behaviour with the `reasoning` `enabled` boolean. [Learn more in our docs](https://openrouter.ai/docs/use-cases/reasoning-tokens#enable-reasoning-with-default-config).\"\r\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774172206618}}
{"type":"message","id":"3de8a225","parentId":"63a5697d","timestamp":"2026-03-22T09:36:55.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"根据 OpenRouter API 返回的数据，小米 MiMo-V2-Pro 现在已经不再免费了！pricing 显示：\n- prompt: $0.000001/1K tokens（输入）\n- completion: $0.000003/1K tokens（输出）\n- input_cache_read: $0.0000002/1K tokens（缓存读取）\n\n这说明之前的免费期已经结束了。我需要如实告诉主人这个情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，有个重要发现！⚠️\n\n## 小米 MiMo-V2-Pro 不再免费了！\n\n根据刚才查到的 OpenRouter 实时数据：\n\n| 模型 | 输入价格 | 输出价格 |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| **MiMo-V2-Pro** | $0.001/1K tokens | $0.003/1K tokens |\n| MiMo-V2-Flash | $0.00009/1K tokens | $0.00029/1K tokens |\n| MiMo-V2-Omni | $0.0004/1K tokens | $0.002/1K tokens |\n\n**免费期已经结束了！** 😅\n\n之前 MEMORY.md 里记录的\"一周免费期\"已过。现在用 MiMo-V2-Pro 是要收费的。\n\n---\n\n## 💡 建议\n\n1. **如果想要便宜** → 切换到 **MiMo-V2-Flash**（价格只有 Pro 的 ~10%，性能也很强，全球开源第一）\n2. **如果想要免费** → 回到 **Qwen3.5-Plus**（阿里云百炼，当前配置显示费用 $0）\n3. **如果继续用 Pro** → 也可以，价格不算贵\n\n主人想怎么选？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":905,"output":501,"cacheRead":168576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":169982,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774172206747}}
