{"type":"message","id":"1d746d1c","parentId":"0c8f5e14","timestamp":"2026-03-22T10:59:16.819Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人授权我直接处理了！这是第一层操作（可逆的内部系统配置），我可以直接执行。\n\n我需要：\n1. 检查 OpenClaw 是否已配置为系统服务\n2. 创建一个外部监控脚本（独立于网关）\n3. 配置自动重启策略\n\n让我先检查当前配置状态，然后创建监控脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！主人放心，我这就去部署自动恢复系统 🦞💪\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_69ffa06e98c04694a3c24e1a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c045132ad72943bbb4a3a089","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774177148918}}
