{"type":"message","id":"5bac7fb6","parentId":"41c2efd5","timestamp":"2026-03-22T10:59:42.302Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到 scripts 目录里已经有一些脚本了。现在我需要：\n1. 检查网关状态\n2. 创建一个看门狗监控脚本（独立于网关）\n3. 配置 Windows 任务计划程序来定期运行监控\n\n让我先检查网关状态，然后创建监控脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fb74c6f9a78844eab10c2fad","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Process -Name \"node\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object {$_.Path -like \"*openclaw*\"} | Select-Object Id, ProcessName, StartTime"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_188608b4b3394bddbfb571a2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"netstat -ano | findstr \":8080\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774177175801}}
