{"type":"message","id":"7b095188","parentId":"4cccabbd","timestamp":"2026-03-22T12:45:42.362Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The direct fetching of the novel content isn't working well. But I already have quite a bit of information from the Baidu search results. Let me try one more source and then compile what I know.\n\nFrom the Baidu search, I found:\n1. Title: 绝对之门 (The Absolute Gate)\n2. Author: 魔性沧月 (Magic Azure Moon / Moxing Cangyue)\n3. Genre: Originally listed as 都市/都市重生 (Urban/Urban Rebirth), later as 科幻推理 (Sci-fi Mystery)\n\n\n4. Status: 连载中 (Ongoing)\n5. Latest chapter: 第三百四十四章全球星门救援网络 (Chapter 344: Global Star Gate Rescue Network)\n6. Last updated: 2026-03-18 or 2026-03-21\n7. Plot: The protagonist accidentally opens a \"天门\" (Heavenly Gate/Portal) that connects to reality, causing creatures from an illusory dimension to invade the real world, adding another apocalyptic threat to a universe already destined for extinction. Chapter 1 is called 一念开天门 (One Thought Opens the Heavenly Gate).\n\nThe early chapters establish the invasion premise with encounters involving supernatural entities and unexplained phenomena, gradually revealing the protagonist's powers and the escalating danger. Chapter 5 marks a critical turning point where death becomes inevitable, leading into what appears to be a larger organization called the Noah Divine Religion with 65 free chapters available.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_80c54564883c47c2b8329918","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"extractMode":"markdown","maxChars":20000,"url":"https://www.69shu.com/44726/index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":697,"output":704,"cacheRead":62720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64121,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774183531985}}
