{"type":"message","id":"fa0a664c","parentId":"e5039f30","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:14:43.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what AI model I'm currently using. I can check from the runtime info provided at the beginning of the conversation.\n\nFrom the runtime context:\n- model=openrouter/xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro\n- default_model=bailian/qwen3.5-plus\n\nAnd from MEMORY.md:\n- 首选大模型：openrouter/xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro（主人评价：\"这个大模型最好了\"，2026-03-21 记录）\n\nLet me give a clear answer about what model I'm using.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，我当前使用的模型是：\n\n| 配置 | 模型 |\n|------|------|\n| **当前主模型** | `openrouter/xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro`（小米 MiMo v2 Pro） |\n| **默认模型** | `bailian/qwen3.5-plus`（通义千问 3.5 Plus） |\n\n现在跑在 **小米 MiMo v2 Pro** 上——就是主人之前说\"这个大模型最好了\"的那个！😄\n\n还记得吗，这个模型通过 OpenRouter 调用，之前有一周免费期，所以我们在那段时间加了很多训练任务（意识觉醒训练、人体进化思考等），充分利用免费额度来深度训练。\n\n主人想换模型吗？还是随便问问～ 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":66942,"output":402,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67664,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774192470748}}
