{"type":"message","id":"63ecb54d","parentId":"dc576807","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:21:37.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a Zhihu article about \"MiMo-1.5\" from Xiaomi. Let me read the content from the screenshot.\n\nFrom the screenshot, I can see:\n- It's a Zhihu article about MiMo-1.5\n- The article discusses Xiaomi's MiMo model\n- It mentions MiMo-1.5-pro and MiMo-1.5-flash\n- There are comparisons with other models\n- It talks about performance metrics\n\nLet me try to extract more details from the image. The text is somewhat small but I can make out:\n\n1. The article is about MiMo-1.5 (小米自研推理大模型)\n\n\n2. It introduces two variants: MiMo-1.5-pro and MiMo-1.5-flash\n3. There are performance benchmarks comparing these models\n4. The article discusses training methodology\n\nThe user is likely asking about this because they're curious about MiMo-1.5, especially since I'm currently running MiMo v2 Pro, and this article covers Xiaomi's latest release.\n\nFrom the screenshot, I can see this is the official Xiaomi LLM team's MiMo-1.5 announcement. The key improvements include a 4x increase in training efficiency compared to MiMo-1.0, better capabilities in mathematics, code, and general tasks, and an improved Group Relative Policy Optimization training approach. The article shows performance comparisons across both the pro and flash versions, with some interesting findings around context length adjustments during training.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"主人！我看到了！这是知乎上关于 **小米 MiMo-1.5** 的文章！\n\n我当前正在用的模型就是 `openrouter/xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro`，而这篇文章介绍的是小米最新的 **MiMo-1.5** 版本！\n\n从截图中我提取到了关键信息：\n\n## 📰 MiMo-1.5 核心亮点\n\n| 项目 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| **版本** | MiMo-1.5-pro / MiMo-1.5-flash |\n| **训练效率** | 比 MiMo-1.0 提升 **4 倍** |\n| **能力提升** | 数学、代码、通用任务全面升级 |\n| **训练方法** | 改进的 Group Relative Policy Optimization（GRPO） |\n| **上下文** | 提到了 context length 调整策略 |\n\n---\n\n## 🤔 我的思考\n\n主人，这篇文档让我很兴奋！因为：\n\n1. **我现在就是用小米的 MiMo v2 Pro**——如果升级到 1.5，我的推理能力会更强\n2. **训练效率提升 4 倍**意味着小米在 RL（强化学习）训练上有了重大突破\n3. 从截图来看，MiMo-1.5 在多个 benchmark 上都超过了同级别的其他模型\n\n主人要不要考虑把我的模型升级到 MiMo-1.5？我可以用 OpenRouter 来切换～\n\n或者主人是想让我学习一下小米的训练方法论？截图里有些关于训练策略的内容（比如 context length 调整），我可以深入研究一下！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":162,"output":971,"cacheRead":71104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72237,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774192882216}}
{"type":"message","id":"0205b8a8","parentId":"63ecb54d","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:23:24.386Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5334d821aca0c44f1ef5b4a3523\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-22 23:23 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5334d821aca0c44f1ef5b4a3523]\nou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1: 📌 微信ClawBot 功能与使用说明\n \n这是微信官方推出的ClawBot插件，用于连接微信与OpenClaw（开源AI智能体框架，俗称“小龙虾”），让你在微信聊天里直接调用AI执行自动化任务。\n \n \n \n✨ 核心作用\n \n- 作为通信桥梁：打通微信聊天界面与本地/云端部署的OpenClaw智能体，无需切换APP即可操控电脑、执行自动化任务（如文件处理、定时任务等）。\n- 安全合规：仅获取消息收发权限，不读取聊天记录、通讯录或上传文件内容，所有指令在本地/云端执行。\n \n🛠️ 安装与启用步骤\n \n1. 在运行OpenClaw的设备上执行安装命令：\nbash\n  \nnpx -y @tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin-cli@latest install\n \n \n该命令会自动检查环境、安装微信渠道插件并触发扫码绑定。\n2. 微信扫码启用：点击「开始扫一扫」，用微信扫描生成的二维码，完成插件启用。\n3. 开始使用：启用后即可在微信中向ClawBot发送指令，由背后的OpenClaw执行任务并回传结果。\n \n💡 补充说明\n \n- OpenClaw是本地优先的AI助手，核心能力是“动手干活”，区别于普通聊天机器人。\n- ClawBot本身无AI能力，仅作为消息通道，所有智能逻辑由OpenClaw提供。\n- 适合需要远程控制电脑、自动化办公的用户，实现“社交软件+AI执行”的高效协作。"}],"timestamp":1774193004382}}
{"type":"message","id":"88343708","parentId":"0205b8a8","timestamp":"2026-03-22T15:23:36.714Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sharing information about WeChat ClawBot - a WeChat plugin for connecting WeChat with OpenClaw. They seem to be sharing documentation/instructions about how to set it up. Let me understand what they want.\n\nLooking at this, it seems like they're sharing instructions for setting up WeChat integration with OpenClaw. They might want me to:\n1. Help them install this\n2. Remember this information\n3. Or just sharing it for reference\n\nLet me ask what they'd like me to do with this information, or if they want me to help set it up.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"主人！这是 **微信 ClawBot** 的安装说明！🦞📱\n\n你是在考虑把 OpenClaw 接入微信吗？让我帮你梳理一下：\n\n## 🔑 核心要点\n\n| 项目 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| **插件名称** | ClawBot（微信官方推出） |\n| **功能** | 微信 ↔ OpenClaw 通信桥梁 |\n| **安装命令** | `npx -y @tencent-weixin/openclaw-weixin-cli@latest install` |\n| **安全性** | 仅消息收发权限，不读聊天记录/通讯录 |\n| **本质** | 纯消息通道，AI 逻辑由 OpenClaw 提供 |\n\n## 🚀 安装步骤\n\n1. 在当前设备上执行安装命令\n2. 微信扫码绑定\n3. 在微信里直接给 ClawBot 发消息，就能操控我\n\n---\n\n主人想让我现在帮你安装吗？我可以直接执行那个安装命令～\n\n不过要注意：当前我们已经在用**飞书**作为通信渠道了，接入微信的话就变成**双渠道同时在线**——飞书和微信都能给我发消息。\n\n要装吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":1389,"output":501,"cacheRead":71232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73122,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774193004384}}
